Name: Puzld
Subtitle: Your pictures, puzzled.
Description:
Turn your photos into puzzles, or unscramble numbered blocks by sliding the pieces into their original sequential order. 

Keep an eye on the timer—try beating your best time on each level! 

Unlock higher levels by solving puzls or purchasing Puzld Coins. More info at Puzld.com.

Stay tuned for updates—Tons of cool new features to come! 

Questions, feature requests, or bugs to report? YOUR FEEDBACK IS APPRECIATED! Let me know via the in-app Feedback button or info@puzld.com.

Name: Lords.io Warfare
Subtitle: Lords.io Warfare
Description: "Pick up gold to buy soldiers or build houses to increase population limit. But don't forget to protect them with towers.\n\nLordz.io Once you get enough ressources, create your faithful soldiers, choosing between soldier, knight, archer, barbarian or dragon, to get the upper hand on other lordz io."

Name: Pressure!
Subtitle: Only the bold survives...
Description:
"Can you handle Pressure!?? 
The Joker is going to challenge you and do its best to keep you distracted.
So this is going to take a lot of concentration & focusing, so be prepared! 

EASY TO PLAY:
• Simply match the large symbol that appears in the center of the screen by tapping on one of your 10 game pieces.
• Collect and use the Wildcards that will parade on the screen, to enhance your game and strategy (The Eliminator).
•\xa0Complete the 5-digit Code to score bonus points (The Eliminator).
• Stage 3 shows the game piece briefly, then hides it behind a question mark, so pay attention!

GAMES:
• The Cooker: An adjustable timed game for 1 or 2 Players.
• The Eliminator: The Ultimate Challenge, the one that will fully test your abilities.

FEATURES:
• Suitable for all ages and genders.
• Addictive, unpredictable and non-repetitive game dynamics, great to help all ages with their focus.
• Helps improve your reflexes and multi-tasking ability.
• It's a great exercise for those with ADD and ADHD issues. Forget that spinning gadget!
• Unlimited levels, compete with yourself or play with your friends!
• OPTIONAL: Login to GameCenter and track your scores and achievements and challenge your friends.

NOTE: You can easily earn Free Play Tickets within the game at no cost to you. 
In-App Purchases are intended as an easy way to thank the Developers, but are not required. Thanks!

PRIVACY NOTICE: This game does not collect any personal information. We value people's privacy.
This app employs Unity Ads, which is governed by their own privacy policy located at: https://unity3d.com/legal/privacy-policy"

Name: Brain Distraction: Tricky Test
Subtitle: "World's Hardest Easiest Game"
Description:
"Brain Distraction is a simple game to learn,  but a tricky game to master. Show some self control, avoid the distractions and select the image that doesn't match the text. All it takes is one-touch! 

Could this be The Worlds Easiest IQ Reversal Game? Perhaps, but if you lack self control and mistakenly allow yourself to be distracted by what Simon says you will soon be selecting the wrong answer.

Test your reaction speed, avoid distractions, and show some brain control. You only get a short period of time to make your decision, putting your reverse logic and reaction speed to the ultimate test. With each level the game gets faster, meaning making a quick response is essential. Click on the wrong answer and it’s game over!

How to play Brain Distraction

- You will see a word at the top of the screen.

-  … And images below.

- One image will match the word.  The other will be a mismatch.

- One-touch on the button that is not the same as the word at the top of the screen.

- Make your decision before the time runs out.

- As the game progresses, time runs out faster and there are more images
to select.


Brain Distraction – Highlights

- Simple to play brain teaser, suitable for anybody.

- Easy one-touch controls.

- Do the opposite of what Simon says.

- Exercise self control - do the opposite of what it and you want to do.

- Test & improve your reaction speed.

- Fast-paced gameplay great for killing time wherever you are!

- Compete against friends online!

- Earn achievements as you play.

Website: http://www.riceburgerlabs.com
Twitter: http://www.twitter.com/RiceBurgerLabs
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/riceburgerlabs/

Brain Distraction is a brain teaser with a twist. Show self control, test your reaction speed and improve your logic skills with this simple to play one-touch reverse logic game. With fun, simple, fast-paced gameplay, Brain Distraction is the perfect way to kill time and exercise your brain!

DOWNLOAD THE WORLDS EASIEST IQ REVERSAL GAME TODAY! HOW HIGH CAN YOU SCORE?"

Name: Skyblock Island Survival Game
Subtitle: Battle Royale multiplayer
Description:
Skyblock Island is the unique multiplayer hit you don’t want to miss! Annihilate your opponents in one-on-one brawls where good strategy and quick reflexes are key to survival! 

BRING YOUR CARDS TO BATTLE

Bring powerful heroes or explosive spells locked away in unique trading cards for you to collect! Shape your deck before the battle and see your strategy blow your enemy away! Find the cards that fit your play-style and put them to the test in one-on-one skirmishes in tight and deadly arenas!

REAL-TIME MULTIPLAYER FIRST PERSON SHOOTER

Make your strategy, then shoot your way through dozens of high-octane maps as you destroy the opposition! Choose your Hero, upgrade your troops, then bring them to the arenas where you will dodge, shoot, and destroy! 

Features:
Multiplayer
Choose your hero
Place your troops and win against your opponents 
Upgrade your cards
In app purchases for spell and unit upgrades
A lot of incredible weapons and skins!

Name: Snake Candy.IO
Subtitle: Creative Snake Candy Battle
Description:
Do you love eating candies?

You will play against other snakes online! Move strategically and glide in front of other snakes to defeat them. Try to get other snakes to bump into you so that you can eat their candy remains to strengthen yourself! Avoid your head touching other snakes, or you will get blast and incarnated into candies as well, then have to start over.

Are you ready to be the biggest snake?

Snake Candy.IO is completely free to play but some in-game items such as skin or diamonds will require payment.

Tips:
- Using your body to hit toward the head of others snakes 
- Slither and eat as many candies as you can to grow larger
- Try to stay alive as long as possible
- Tap the lightening button to speed up
- Avoid the map margins or you will explode and turn out to be candies

Features:
- Fun Online Multiplayer Snake Game
- Compete with Worldwide Players in Single Fight
- More updates and game modes like team fight and scuffle are coming up soon
- Various Cute Snake Skins, Fun for all ages
- Sweetest snake game: Keep eating candies & grow bigger
- Multi chances to revive. No one knows who will be the winner untill the end
- Enjoy a lag free and smooth gaming experience
- Easy and fun to start, even more fun to fully master

Start and spread the fun in Snake Candy.IO for FREE now!!

Follow us to get news and updates on facebook:
https://www.facebook.com/Snake-CandyIO-343437352806758/
- Acquire up to date Snake Candy.IO game news and updates
- Special rewards and events all the time
